item.title: Sessions
item.description: There are 3 major sessions that Enigma conducts regularly through out the month. These sessions are generally organised by the members of the Club itself. If you have an idea for a new session or want to take one yourself, get in touch with us on Discord. The details for each session can be found below: Competitive Coding Session Mondays | 6 - 8pm | LT-2 The Competitive Coding session aims to take the programming skills of the members of the club to the next level.
